---
title: BBQ-Spiced Grilled Barramundi with Corn on the Cob, Zucchini and Peppers
description: We love BBQ-spiced everything and barramundi is the perfect fish to soak in all the smoky flavours! Served with an extra drizzle of BBQ sauce plus a hearty helping of delicious grilled veggies!
